text = "Welcome to Bullet Pong! The bullet hell pong game.

The goal is to score on the enemy player 
until they run out of lives. If you run out of lives it's GAME OVER. 
Use your paddle to block the ball and stop it from going into
your goal. Watch out for the different types of balls!

You can control your paddle by either the mouse or the keyboard.

Mouse is recommended for higher difficulties!

If using the keyboard use the following keys:
W: Move Up
S: Move Down
A (Hold): Speed Up
D (Hold): Slow Down

Click on the ball types button to see the different balls 
you will encounter. Each one has special rules."
